# AI Model Gateway 🚀

A production-style AI Model Gateway built with FastAPI, supporting multiple large language model providers with a unified OpenAI-like interface and streaming response capability.

---

## 📌 Overview

This project is an AI gateway that abstracts multiple LLM providers into a single standardized API layer.  
It enables seamless switching between models without changing client-side logic.

---

## ✨ Key Features

- 🔌 Multi-model support (DeepSeek / Qwen / GLM / Kimi)
- 🔁 Unified API interface (OpenAI-style design)
- 🌊 Streaming response via SSE (Server-Sent Events)
- 🧠 Model routing layer (extensible architecture)
- ⚙️ Environment-based configuration (.env)
- 🧩 Modular provider system (plug & play design)
- 🚀 Lightweight FastAPI backend

---

## 🧠 Supported Models

| Provider   | Status |
|------------|--------|
| DeepSeek   | ✅ |
| Qwen       | ✅ |
| GLM        | ✅ |
| Kimi       | ✅ |

---

## 🏗️ Architecture


Client
↓
FastAPI Gateway
↓
Model Router Layer
↓
Provider Adapters
↓
DeepSeek / Qwen / GLM / Kimi APIs


